data.description: Move in ready 4 bedroom, 4 bath two story pool home with over 3,000 sq.ft. of living space. Located in the gated community of Olympia Pointe. Home features Corian counters with a large island, 42" upper cabinets, stainless steel appliances, central vac, intercom/music system, alarm system and a jetted tub in the master bath. Olympia Pointe has a community center with pool table, kitchen and exercise room. Also a large heated pool, spa, kiddie pool and tot lot. A great place to call home.
